com.mmm.cms.homehealth.hipps

Class HIPPSCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mmm.cms.homehealth.hipps.HIPPSCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HIPPSCodeIF
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HIPPSCode_2015, HIPPSCode_2016, HIPPSCode_2017, HIPPSCode_2018, HIPPSCode_2019

    public class HIPPSCode
extends java.lang.Object
implements HIPPSCodeIF
    This holds the 5 character HIPPS code based on the 5 elements of:
    • episode timing
    • Grouping steps
    • clinical Score
    • functionalScore
    • nrsScore
    Author:
    3M Health Information Systems for CMS Home Health
